{
  "stem": "1917.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just didn't want to end up like these children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I realized that if I wasn't going to take any action.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was going to end up there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know what to do, how to survive in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were no rules.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were no briefings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were no-- only rumors and experience.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's all there was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I started watching the other girls, other children who had been there a little bit longer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I found out that the best way to get any food was to become an organizer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "To organize in the Auschwitz language meant stealing from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the best place to organize was to go to the kitchen and steal some potatoes, or organize some potatoes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Potatoes seemed to be the miracle food in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] They would choose every morning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Our-- our morning would start, first of all, we would get up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the following day, we got up about five o'clock.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We straightened out our bed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And by six o'clock-- and we helped some of the younger children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Some of them were only one years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There were no mothers in that barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In spite of whatever you read in any books, there were no mothers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The oldest child was 13.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we would go outside for roll call.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The roll call lasted anywhere from half an hour to six, and at one occasion, eight hours.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Everybody had to be accounted for regardless of their condition, regardless of the fact if they were alive or dead.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So those three dead children that I saw on the bathroom in the latrine that night, they were placed in front of the group.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
